<p>Hello <%= @resource.p_fname %>!</p>

<p>A request was made to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>
<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email and nothing will be changed on your account.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @token) %></p>

<p>Again, none of your information will change unless you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
